description: Genuine Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) parts! This ice container slide rail (part number WR72X10233) is for refrigerators. Ice container slide rail WR72X10233 supports the ice container as the ice container slides in and out. Unplug the refrigerator and safely store any food that could deteriorate while the power is off before installing this part. Wear work gloves to protect your hands.
